LONGTEXTS.cdbdd_userdefined_view_txt_1: SELECT personalnummer, day, day_type_id, description, capacity, day_off, is_resource, org_id FROM ( SELECT personalnummer personalnummer, days.day day, days.day_type_id day_type_id, days.description description, CASE WHEN days.user_capacity IS NOT NULL THEN days.user_capacity ELSE days.base_capacity * (1 - dt.is_day_off_type) END capacity, dt.is_day_off_type day_off, is_resource is_resource, org_id org_id FROM ( SELECT a.personalnummer personalnummer, b.day day, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != chr(1) THEN u.day_type_id ELSE b.day_type_id END  day_type_id, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != chr(1) THEN u.description ELSE b.description END  description, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != chr(1) THEN u.capacity ELSE NULL END  user_capacity, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != chr(1) THEN NULL ELSE a.capacity END  base_capacity, a.is_resource is_resource, a.org_id org_id FROM cdb_calendar_entry b CROSS JOIN angestellter a LEFT JOIN cdb_calendar_user_entry_v u ON b.day = u.day AND u.personalnummer = a.personalnummer WHERE a.calendar_profile_id = b.calendar_profile_id AND a.calendar_profile_id IS NOT NULL AND a.calendar_profile_id != chr(1) AND b.calendar_profile_id IS NOT NULL AND b.calendar_profile_id != chr(1) AND (b.cdb_project_id IS NULL OR b.cdb_project_id = chr(1)) ) days JOIN  cdb_day_type dt ON  days.day_type_id = dt.day_type_id ) t
LONGTEXTS.cdbdd_userdefined_view_txt_5: SELECT  personalnummer, day, day_type_id, description, capacity, day_off, is_resource, org_id FROM ( SELECT personalnummer personalnummer, days.day day, days.day_type_id day_type_id, days.description description, CASE WHEN days.user_capacity IS NOT NULL THEN days.user_capacity ELSE days.base_capacity * (1 - dt.is_day_off_type) END capacity, dt.is_day_off_type day_off, is_resource is_resource, org_id org_id FROM ( SELECT a.personalnummer personalnummer, b.day day, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN u.day_type_id ELSE b.day_type_id END  day_type_id, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN u.description ELSE b.description END  description, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN u.capacity ELSE NULL END  user_capacity, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN NULL ELSE a.capacity END  base_capacity, a.is_resource is_resource, a.org_id org_id FROM cdb_calendar_entry b CROSS JOIN angestellter a LEFT JOIN cdb_calendar_user_entry_v u ON b.day = u.day AND u.personalnummer = a.personalnummer WHERE a.calendar_profile_id = b.calendar_profile_id AND a.calendar_profile_id IS NOT NULL AND a.calendar_profile_id != '' AND b.calendar_profile_id IS NOT NULL AND b.calendar_profile_id != '' AND (b.cdb_project_id IS NULL OR b.cdb_project_id = '') ) days JOIN  cdb_day_type dt ON  days.day_type_id = dt.day_type_id ) t
LONGTEXTS.cdbdd_userdefined_view_txt_6: SELECT personalnummer, day, day_type_id, description, capacity, day_off, is_resource, org_id FROM ( SELECT personalnummer personalnummer, days.day day, days.day_type_id day_type_id, days.description description, CASE WHEN days.user_capacity IS NOT NULL THEN days.user_capacity ELSE days.base_capacity * (1 - dt.is_day_off_type) END capacity, dt.is_day_off_type day_off, is_resource is_resource, org_id org_id FROM ( SELECT a.personalnummer personalnummer, b.day day, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN u.day_type_id ELSE b.day_type_id END  day_type_id, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN u.description ELSE b.description END  description, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN u.capacity ELSE NULL END  user_capacity, CASE WHEN u.personalnummer IS NOT NULL AND u.personalnummer != '' THEN NULL ELSE a.capacity END  base_capacity, a.is_resource is_resource, a.org_id org_id FROM cdb_calendar_entry b CROSS JOIN angestellter a LEFT JOIN cdb_calendar_user_entry_v u ON b.day = u.day AND u.personalnummer = a.personalnummer WHERE a.calendar_profile_id = b.calendar_profile_id AND a.calendar_profile_id IS NOT NULL AND a.calendar_profile_id != '' AND b.calendar_profile_id IS NOT NULL AND b.calendar_profile_id != '' AND (b.cdb_project_id IS NULL OR b.cdb_project_id = '') ) days JOIN  cdb_day_type dt ON  days.day_type_id = dt.day_type_id ) t
